par.note:
The method needs to be called only in the case if unmanaged image was allocated
            using  method. In the case if the class instance was created using constructor,
            this method does not free unmanaged memory.

member.summary:
Define implicit cast between DirectShowLib.DsLong and System.Int64 for languages supporting this feature.
VB.Net doesn't support implicit cast.  for similar functionality.

  // Define a new DsLong instance
  DsLong dsL = new DsLong(9876543210);
  // Do implicit cast between DsLong and Int64
  long l = dsL;

  Console.WriteLine(l.ToString());

